import React, {useState} from 'react'
import { BrowserRouter, Routes, Route } from 'react-router-dom'
import Home from './components/AreaPublica/Home'
import Viagens from './components/AreaPublica/Viagens'
import InscreverSe from './components/AreaPublica/InscreverSe'
import Login from './components/AreaRestrita/Login'
import AreaAdm from './components/AreaRestrita/AreaAdm'
import CriarViagem from './components/AreaRestrita/CriarViagem'
import ViagemEscolhida from './components/AreaRestrita/ViagemEscolhida'


export default function App() {
  
  return (
    <BrowserRouter>
    <Routes>
      <Route index element = {<Home/>}/>
      <Route path = "viagens" element = {<Viagens/>}/>
      <Route path = "cadastro" element = {<InscreverSe/>}/>
      <Route path = "login" element = {<Login/>}/>
      <Route path = "adm" element = {<AreaAdm/>}/>
      <Route path = "criar" element = {<CriarViagem/>}/>
      <Route path = "cadastrados" element = {<ViagemEscolhida/>}/>
    </Routes>
    </BrowserRouter>
 )
}
